# Copy to .env for local API testing (e.g. `vercel dev`), or set in Vercel →
# Project → Settings → Environment Variables for production.
#
# Powers the "Ask Ajinkya" AI assistant (api/chat.js). Without it, the assistant
# returns a friendly fallback instead of live answers — the site still works.
# Get a key at https://console.anthropic.com
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=
